<h3>Alison Price, Environmental Manager, CarTakeBack.com</h3>

<p>'CarTakeBack are pleased to support the Mayor of London's van scrappage scheme ahead of the introduction of the ULEZ. All efforts need to be made in order to help tackle London's air quality crisis, and this initiative helps the city move towards clean air whilst supporting those most affected by the introduction of the ULEZ.</p>

<p>'Scrapping your van with CarTakeBack will ensure you receive the DVLA Certificate of Destruction required to complete your application to receive the funding from TfL. Get an instant, no obligation quote with CarTakeBack - we'll pay you a great price for your old van and offer free collection from any address.'</p> 
