<p>'It is Drivy's mission to get people to give up their personal cars. Using shared cars only when needed means less parked cars on the road, cleaner air and more space in the city. With vehicles are sourced from private car owners and dedicated fleets, all rentals are covered with fully comprehensive insurance and 24/7 breakdown assistance.'</p> 
